      "remarks": "This sequence was constructed by Rosen. Note that the number of solutions to $a_i+a_j\\leq x$ is always at least $x$ by construction, but Erd\\H{o}s and Rosen could not even prove whether it is at most $(1+o(1))x$.\n\nThe sequence begins\\[0,1,3,5,9,13,17,24,31,38,45,\\ldots.\\]"
    },
